extendedInfo.description: Whatever sins we did in our previous birth,by this reason we have to face difficulties and problems in this birth.Whatever the problems you are facing in life,this is either any disease or enemy problem,either the problem of money/employment or debt,problem of education or carrier,problem of marriage or relationship,Mahadasha or sadhe-sati of SATURN,MARS is affected or Mangli Dosha in Horoscope,these all problems can be removed in a very easy way by the grace of LORD HANUMAN!Now question arises,How can we achieve this?Whatever the treatment/remedy are given hereby,is very easy and effective and this is the research of our long time experience.
